data.description:
Beautiful contemporary 1 1/2 story 3 bedroom 2 bath house situated on huge corner lot in Sherwood Forest. Living space is 1870 sq.ft. Spacious kitchen, dining room, den with cathedral ceiling, wet bar, wood burning fireplace, large master with walk-in closet. Loft above kitchen could be used as 4th bedroom. Attic storage. Oversize 2 car garage with attic storage. Privacy fence. House has Florida heat pump, whole house fan, hardwood floors in hallway with recessed floor in den. Ceramic floors in kitchen, dining room, & foyer. Marble floors in master & guest bathrooms. Ceiling fans through entire house. New dishwasher, microwave, and disposal. A/C compressor replaced last year. Roof replaced 2 years ago. Beautiful custom wood deck off kitchen & master. Large covered side porch off den. Small balcony off loft above kitchen. Water feature in backyard. The lot beside the home is included in the sale price, making the lot size just under 3/4 acre at 0.71. House is available at any time. Have many more pictures to share. Please call 910-787-4364 for info. 

Neighborhood Description

Nice quiet, peaceful neighborhood with good neighbors. Park with playground within 100yds of home. Close to shopping.
